# StopWindowsTracking

StopWindowsTracking is a simple tool that stops Windows from tracking you and can also remove Windows bloatware.

![screenshot](http://i.imgur.com/1zZAqOt.png)


## Download

[Download the compiled exe here](https://github.com/aStonedPenguin/StopWindowsTracking/releases)

**Note:** You need .NET 4.7 and 64 bit version of Windows installed

## How to Use

Run the exe as admin, select which bloatware and which methods you'd like to use to stop tracking, click run, restart your computer and you're done!